headline: Bull of the Day: Zebra Technologies Corporation (ZBRA)
summary: ZBRA has doubled the S&P 500 over the past 10 years and crushed its Industrial Products sector. Yet, Zebra Technologies stock trades 33% below its records even as the market is at all-time highs and appears a bit frothy in the near term.
